wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.ZS.def: Female population 65 years of age or older as a percentage of the total female population. Population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship.
wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.ZS.name: Population ages 65 and above
wdi2-SP.POP.65UP.FE.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates based on age/sex distributions of United Nations Population Division's World Population Prospects: 2019 Revision.
